sorcer.core.proxy

Interface RemotePartner

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Administrable, Outer, Partner, Remote, Service
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GroupManagement

    public interface RemotePartner
extends Partner, Remote
    Remote servers and other compound remote proxies using inner proxies to extend their functionality via calls on the inner proxies implement this interface. To provide service-to-service functionality this interface extends Service.
    Author:
    Mike Sobolewski
